titles.title: A bill to provide for the liquidation or reliquidation of certain entries relating to fiberboard entered in September through December, 2005.
A bill to provide for the liquidation or reliquidation of certain entries relating to fiberboard entered in September through December, 2005.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: Directs the Bureau of Customs and Border Protection to provide for the liquidation or reliquidation of certain entries relating to fiberboard.
